<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>كِتَابُ الطَّلَاقِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> يُكْرَهُ:</span> بِلَا حَاجَةٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيُبَاحُ:</span> لَهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيُسَنُّ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- لِتَضَرُّرِهَا بِالوَطْءِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَتَرْكِهَا صَلَاةً، وَعِفَّةً، وَنَحْوَهُمَا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَلَا يَصِحُّ إِلَّا مِنْ زَوْجٍ، وَلَوْ مُمَيِّزًا يَعْقِلُهُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَمَنْ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- عُذِرَ بِزَوَالِ عَقْلِهِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- أَوْ أُكْرِهَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- أَوْ هُدِّدَ مِنْ قَادِرٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">فَطَلَّقَ لِذَلِكَ:</span> لَمْ يَقَعْ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَمَنْ صَحَّ طَلَاقُهُ:</span> صَحَّ تَوْكِيلُهُ فِيهِ، وَتَوَكُّلُهُ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- وَيَصِحُّ تَوْكِيلُ امْرَأَةٍ فِي طَلَاقِ نَفْسِهَا، وَغَيْرِهَا <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) قوله: (نفسها، وغيرها) سقطت (ب).</p> </div>